<codeline><highlight class="normal">Data<sp/>structures<sp/>for<sp/>efficient<sp/>entity<sp/>management<sp/>and<sp/>querying.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>module<sp/>provides<sp/>core<sp/>data<sp/>structures<sp/>used<sp/>for<sp/>managing<sp/>GameObjects<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>helios<sp/>engine.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**Components:**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**GameObjectPool**<sp/>-<sp/>Low-level<sp/>O(1)<sp/>object<sp/>pooling<sp/>for<sp/>entity<sp/>recycling.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**GameObjectPoolId**<sp/>-<sp/>Strongly-typed<sp/>identifier<sp/>for<sp/>referencing<sp/>pools.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**GameObjectPoolRegistry**<sp/>-<sp/>Central<sp/>registry<sp/>managing<sp/>multiple<sp/>pools<sp/>by<sp/>ID.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>**GameObjectFilter**<sp/>-<sp/>Bitmask<sp/>enum<sp/>for<sp/>filtering<sp/>entities<sp/>by<sp/>active/inactive<sp/>state<sp/>and<sp/>component<sp/>state.</highlight></codeline>
